				<title>SCP-4416: Tails of Site-42: Why The Foundation Punches Sharks</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8601274/scp-4416#post-4059629</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 15 Nov 2018 19:32:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><strong>SCP-4416:</strong> Tails of Site-42: Why The Foundation Punches Sharks<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580933097" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p>This is the dumbest thing I'll ever write.</p> <p>This SCP is for <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/draft-swap-hub">Draft Swap</a></strong>! The draft I received was from <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hotcoles" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3997195&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580933097" alt="HotColes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3997195)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hotcoles" >HotColes</a></span>, but I ended up writing something completely different. Without him, I wouldn't have been able to come up with this insane idea. I had a lot of fun making this, and spent a lot of time just laughing at the absurdity.</p> <p>Oh, and this is the only article that's tagged both &quot;<strong><tt>shark-punching-center</tt></strong>&quot; and &quot;<strong><tt>dado</tt></strong>&quot;. You're welcome.</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Thanks&nbsp;and&nbsp;Image&nbsp;Attribution</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Special Thanks &#8212; Critters &amp; Beta Readers</strong></span></p> <p>▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580933097" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span><br /> ▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1507289&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580933097" alt="Meserach" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1507289)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" >Meserach</a></span><br /> ▶ HumidHermit (account deleted)<br /> ▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stallmantic" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3472766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580933097" alt="Stallmantic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3472766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stallmantic" >Stallmantic</a></span><br /> ▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580933097" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" >Westrin</a></span><br /> ▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2048131&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580933097" alt="Proasek" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2048131)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" >Proasek</a></span><br /> ▶ <span class="printuser ava